-- EU Nears One-Year Rescue Boost to $1.3 Trillion
-- B y
-- 2012-03-29T08:15:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-29/eu-nears-one-year-rescue-boost-to-1-3-trillion.html
European governments are preparing 
for a one-year increase in the ceiling on rescue aid to 940 
billion euros ($1.3 trillion) to keep the debt crisis at bay, 
according to a draft statement written for finance ministers. 
(Source: Bloomberg)   Running Time: 02:05
 